    {
      "text": "Cool Boarders 4 is a 1999 snowboarding video game developed by Idol Minds and published by Sony Computer Entertainment for the PlayStation. 989 Studios released it in North America while UEP Systems, the creator of the Cool Boarders series, released it in Japan.\nIn the game, the player can play multiple tracks with multiple characters. The campaign includes scenarios such as slalom runs and time attacks. In the game, the feature of multiplayer is also accessible.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Cool Boarders 4 est un jeu vidéo de sport développé par Idol Minds et édité par 989 Studios, sorti en 1999 sur PlayStation.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    },
    {
      "text": "Cool Boarders 4 — компьютерная игра в жанре спортивного симулятора, разработанная Idol Minds и изданная 989 Studios для PlayStation.",
